Translation 2

Long ago Prometheus, the first son of Lapetus, came out of mud to fashion

At the same time Vulcanus came out of mud to make a women.

This women Minerva gave her soul and all to the god of misery.

For that reason her name was Pandora.

Pandora from Iove in Epimetheo gave him marriage.

Their daughter of Pyrrha, was the first mortal. 
